      "text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\">A 67-year-old man, who is an avid gardener, presents at an emergency department. He is suffering from spastic paralysis, which began in his right hand and now extends to his jaw muscles. The causative agent of this infection produces a virulence factor with which of the following activities?</span></p>",
      "unique_key": "Q112565",
